    Packages
    Package
    Description
    accounts.ui
    This package provides user interfaces for logging in and account management.
    accounts.util
    This package provides classes to validate inputs for account management and a class to represent users.
    common.ui
    Provides templates of UI pages needed across the application.
    common.util
    Provides utilities used across the application AND by the pages in common.ui.
    databasePart1
    Contains the interface between the H2 database and the CSE360Monday25 Q and A application.
    main
    Application entry point.
    messaging.ui
    This package contains the UI pages related to direct message functionality.
    messaging.util
    This package contains backend classes for direct messaging, including the message class, a collection class for messages, and input validation.
    questions.ui
    Contains the UI pages for functionality related to questions, answers, and reviews.
    questions.util
    Contains backend classes needed for questions, answers, and reviews.
    test.accounts.util
    Contains unit tests for utility classes for the accounts package.
    test.database
    JUnit tests for databasePart1
    test.legacy
    Contains unit tests for functionality implemented before the TP3 phase.
